person
↓
story
↓
conversation
↓
another mind

Memes propagate across a network of people.

⸻

7. AI webs

AI models themselves are giant connection webs.

Transformers (like me) operate with layers of connections that move patterns through the network.

token
→ attention web
→ transformed token

Meaning emerges from relationships between nodes.

