Why webs keep appearing

Webs solve three big problems at once:

1. Resilience

Damage to one node doesn’t collapse the system.

2. Signal propagation

Information can travel quickly through multiple paths.

3. Emergent intelligence

Complex patterns emerge from simple connections.

